data.description: This charming Clawson Colonial offers a warm and inviting atmosphere, making it the perfect home for new owners. The property boasts a thoughtful layout with both a living and family room, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment.The bright kitchen is a highlight, featuring tile flooring and modern stainless-steel appliances. It seamlessly opens up into the family room, where cathedral ceilings create an airy and spacious feel. The focal point of the family room is a brick natural fireplace, adding a cozy touch to the space.The front room is adorned with a picture window that bathes the interior in natural light, enhancing the overall brightness of the home. Convenience is key with a first-floor laundry/mudroom, offering practicality for daily tasks.The property sits on a generous lot size, with the added benefit of a fenced-in yard, providing both privacy and a secure space for outdoor activities. The location is ideal, with proximity to restaurants, shopping centers, parks, and more, ensuring a convenient and enjoyable lifestyle.For families, the elementary school and preschool are within walking distance, adding to the appeal of the neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home – schedule your showing today and discover the charm and comfort that await you in this Clawson Colonial.**Furnace, Hot Water Tank, AC are all brand new as of Sept 2022.BATVAI Contact LaShawn and Towanna for all questions.
